item.title: CVE-2021-24341|2024-08-03T19:28:23.417Z -- unknown -- xllentech%20english%20islamic%20calendar
item.description: When deleting a date in the Xllentech English Islamic Calendar WordPress plugin before 2.6.8, the year_number and month_number POST parameters are not sanitised, escaped or validated before being used in a SQL statement, leading to SQL injection.
